## Examples and Use Cases

- The concept of *Ubuntu* cannot be translated as “community”—its internal ethics and logic are irreducible  
- An intelligence shaped by embodiment cannot be collapsed into data streams  
- Loss of irreducibility is a key factor in cultural erasure and AI flattening
